name: Whereabouts Known
description:
The trail returns to the valley of stone,
Giants bathe in moonlight,
Like water memories flow.


My first illustrative mint on his et nunc, in memory of a captivating place from my childhood. Airdropped to addresses owning any of the Whereabouts Unknown 1-10 on a snapshot conducted 17.12.21.

2048x2048 digital illustration.
